strings: <voice_0x010011AE><se_def>*: Don't come any closer!

<voice_0x010011AF><se_def>*: I don't know who you are,
but I won't let you hurt Master Dominico!

<voice_0x010011B0><se_low>Dominico: What are you mumbling about, David!?
What could you possibly do to protect me,
you useless good-for-nothing!
<voice_0x010011B1><se_low>Dominico: Move!
<voice_0x010011B2><se_def>David: O-Of course, Master!

<voice_0x010011B3><se_low>Dominico: ...Listen to me, girl!
I am Dominico, the great magician!
I presume you have come for me.
<voice_0x010011B4><se_low>Dominico: Well I regret to inform you that I knew you were coming! I foretold this encounter!
<voice_0x010011B5><se_low>Dominico: Consequently, I have already mastered the spell necessary to eliminate a pesky little wand-waver like you!

<voice_0x010011B6><se_low>Dominico: So away with you!
Go back to where you came from!
...Alakazam!
<voice_0x010011B7><se_high>Jessica: Hwa ha ha!

<voice_0x010011B8><se_high>Jessica: Such a pity...you can't see how useless your
feeble enchantments are against the might
of this sceptre!
<voice_0x010011B9><se_high>Jessica: Already it has claimed the lives of four heirs.
<voice_0x010011BA><se_low>Dominico: ...W-What!?

<voice_0x010011BB><se_low>Dominico: Enough of your trickery!
Nothing can resist my magic!
Alakazam!
<voice_0x010011BC><se_high>Jessica: It is time to end this! Watching you struggle on in vain is just too pitiful...
<voice_0x010011BD><se_high>Jessica: ...What's this!?
<voice_0x010011BE><se_high>Jessica: Well, you were quicker than I expected.
<voice_0x010011BF><se_high>Jessica: He he! Well, it seems your pathetic circle has helped you after all. If it hadn't bought you some time, you'd already be dead.

<voice_0x010011C0><se_high>Jessica: Don't worry, you're safe...for now.
I'm not in the mood to take you all on at once.
I just haven't got it in me.
<voice_0x010011C1><se_high>Jessica: If I were you, I'd prepare a sturdier defence for our next meeting! And perhaps a shroud!

<voice_0x010011C2><se_low>Dominico: Hahh...hahh...
That...hahh...that was a narrow escape!
<voice_0x010011C3><se_def>David: M-Master Dominico! Are you hurt!?

<voice_0x010011C4><se_low>Dominico: Get off me, you disgusting piece of filth!
This isn't a chance for you to wheedle your way into my good books!
<voice_0x010011C5><se_def>David: I, I wasn't trying to... I, I just...
<voice_0x010011C6><se_low>Dominico: Enough! Go and give Sir Leopold his dinner! Can't you see I have business to attend to!?
<voice_0x010011C7><se_def>David: O-Of course, Master!
<voice_0x010011C8><se_low>Dominico: You! It seems I am indebted to you! Come!
